PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774353808
OL,3,CHow the recent wet weather is
OL,4,Cthreatening UK's bee population
OL,6,FMild temperatures have also resulted
OL,7,Fin more predatory wasps being around.
OL,8,FThey would not usually survive the
OL,9,Fcold winter, but they have been
OL,10,Fdestroying the bee colonies in man-
OL,11,Fmade hives and in the wild because of
OL,12,Fthe warmth.
OL,14,FDr Harry Siviter, an expert in bee
OL,15,Fbehaviour, ecology and conservation
OL,16,Fsays some of the UK's 270 bee species
OL,17,Fare doing better than others.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774353808
OL,3,CHow the recent wet weather is
OL,4,Cthreatening UK's bee population
OL,6,FHe said: "I do worry about our
OL,7,Fbumblebees in particular. Bees are
OL,8,Fabsolutely essential for our wild
OL,9,Fspaces but also our food production.
OL,11,F"About 75% of the food that we eat in
OL,12,Fterms of the number of crops that we
OL,13,Fgrow require animal pollination and
OL,14,Fbees are really important for that.
OL,16,F"So if we have less bees, in terms of
OL,17,Fthe number of bees and also the
OL,18,Fdiversity of bees, then that will have
OL,19,Fsevere negative impacts on our food
OL,20,Fproduction and wild spaces.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774353808
OL,3,CHow the recent wet weather is
OL,4,Cthreatening UK's bee population
OL,6,F"We live in a world where we don't
OL,7,Fhave a lot of control over the
OL,8,Fenvironment and climate change."
OL,10,F'A changing climate'
OL,12,FAt Stoke Abbott in Dorset, a teaching
OL,13,Fgroup called the Dorset Bee has lost
OL,14,Faround 50 per cent of its hives this
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FBeekeeper Helen Balter-Griffin said:
OL,18,F"This year has been really devastating
OL,19,Ffor us. We are so sad because we spend
OL,20,Ftime observing the bees... It is
OL,21,Freally deeply saddening for us.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774353808
OL,3,CHow the recent wet weather is
OL,4,Cthreatening UK's bee population
OL,6,F"As a beekeeper, one of the first
OL,7,Fthings you really start to notice is
OL,8,Fyour connection to nature and how
OL,9,Feverything is connected. As soon as
OL,10,Fyou see these connections, you can't
OL,11,Funsee them, and it keeps me awake at
OL,12,Fnight, this stress of well, the
OL,13,Fpressure that nature is under."
OL,15,FBeekeeper Gareth Flux added: "This was
OL,16,Fa strong colony coming into the
OL,17,Fautumn, and we noticed in the autumn
OL,18,Fthat they were under pressure from
OL,19,Fwasps and also from the very wet
OL,20,Fwinter we had.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774353808
OL,3,CHow the recent wet weather is
OL,4,Cthreatening UK's bee population
OL,6,F"The bees have become damp, and the
OL,7,Fbees that were weakened by the wasp
OL,8,Fattacks were then unable to sustain
OL,9,Fthe hive temperature.
OL,11,F"So this winter we've just had has
OL,12,Freally been difficult, which is why
OL,13,Fwe've lost good, strong colonies that
OL,14,Fwe would normally expect to survive
OL,15,Fthe winter.
OL,17,F"They can't make it to spring. They're
OL,18,Fjust weakened over time and dwindle.
OL,19,FWe find isome bees in the bottom of
OL,20,Fthe box. These are big strong colonies
OL,21,Fthat shouldn't have a problem,
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774353808
OL,3,CHow the recent wet weather is
OL,4,Cthreatening UK's bee population
OL,6,F"It's forcing change upon us, and we
OL,7,Fhave to adapt to the changes that are
OL,8,Fhappening. So we have to do different
OL,9,Fthings in the coming winters because
OL,10,Fit looks like this is what we've got
OL,11,Fnow."
OL,13,FHow to help bees
OL,15,F"You can help bees quite easily by
OL,16,Fjust planting flowers in your garden,
OL,17,Fand that's something that a lot of
OL,18,Fpeople have access to," adds Dr Harry
OL,19,FSiviter.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774353808
OL,3,CHow the recent wet weather is
OL,4,Cthreatening UK's bee population
OL,6,F"If you have green space or an
OL,7,Fallotment, try to have those flowers
OL,8,Fconsistent throughout the year, and
OL,9,Fthat can really help your local bee
OL,10,Fpopulation.
OL,12,F"Dandelions are one of the most
OL,13,Fimportant nectar sources for bees
OL,14,Fthroughout most of the year."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
